text: Funke Akindele is a Nigerian actress and Film producer. She was popularly known for Jenifa's Diary in 2015. ==Early life== She started alongside Folarin Falana, Juliana Olayode, Lota Chukwu, Paschaline Alex Okoli, Aderounmu Adejumoke, Michael Uba, Tobi Makinde in Jenifa's Diary. ==Selected Filmography== * A Tribe Called Judah * Omo Ghetto ==Reference== Category:Nigerian actors Category:1977 births Category:Living people
